OL,3,CMum admits killing her six-year-old
OL,4,Cson and attempting to murder her father
OL,6,FA mother has pleaded guilty to the
OL,7,Fmanslaughter of her son after he was
OL,8,Ffound dead at a Swansea property in
OL,9,FAugust 2024.
OL,11,FAlexander Zurawski was six years old
OL,12,Fand described as a kind and well-
OL,13,Fbehaved child by his family.
OL,15,FSpeaking via an interpreter in court,
OL,16,FKarolina Zurawska, 41, from Gendros,
OL,17,Falso pleaded guilty to the attempted
OL,18,Fmurder of her father, Krzysztof Siwi.
