OL,6,FSwansea Crown Court heard how Zurawska
OL,7,Fwas suffering from paranoid
OL,8,Fschizoprehnia and pleas on the ground
OL,9,Fof diminished responsibility were
OL,10,Fentered.
OL,12,FSentencing will take place on 25 April.
OL,14,FIn a statement issued by South Wales
OL,15,FPolice following his death,
OL,16,FAlexander's family described him as a
OL,17,F"very kind child".
OL,19,F"Alexander was always well-behaved and
OL,20,Fnever naughty," they said.
